HEADWORD: Tetrathionic
<hw>Tet`ra*thi*on"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Tetra-</ets> + <ets>thionic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or designating, a thionic derivative,
